nodes.text:
Ralph Morse (born June 1, 1955) is an actor. He appeared as an unnamed stormtrooper on Endor in Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi, and also as an Imperial crewman named Derdram, and as a Rebel trooper in Star Wars: Episode V The Empire Strikes Back.
He also played various stormtroopers in both Episode V and Episode VI.
